- Title tag
- Meta description
- URL
- H1 tag
- First 100 words
- Image alt tags
- Throughout content (but donâ€™t overdo it!)

### ğŸ” 7. Keep Updating
SEO is not one-time. Keep finding new keywords, tracking trends, and updating your content.

